<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">This sample illustrates the way to apply formatting to Grid cells based on certain conditions.</Paragraph>

<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center"><Image Source="images/ConditionalFormattingDemo.PNG" Stretch="None" /></Paragraph>
<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center" FontFamily="Cambria" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="14">OlapGrid applied with conditional formats</Paragraph>
<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List Margin="20,20,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph  FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">OlapGrid cells are formatted based on the following conditions:</Paragraph>
<List Margin="20,20,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"><Bold>Red cells</Bold> display sales below $2,000. </Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"><Bold>Yellow cells</Bold> display sales between $200,000-400,000. </Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14"><Bold>Green cells</Bold> display sales that hit a target of $7,500,000. </Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>


